id="iii.ix.xi-p17.1"></span>

<span id="iii.ix.xi-p18"></span> The Greek and Latin texts of Irenæus
add at this point widely variant lists of these words, but in both lists
the words are quite meaningless.

<span id="fn_1076"></span>[183:1077](2010120.htm#fr_1076.md) <span
id="iii.ix.xi-p19.1"></span>

<span id="iii.ix.xi-p20"></span> On Hyginus, see the previous chapter,
